title: Brown Sugar Baking Company
description: No storefront, appointment only bakery. A vegan baking facility that's dedicated peanut- and tree nut-free. Makes cookies, brownies, cupcakes, cinnamon rolls, and cakes; gluten-free options. Sells its products next door at The Urban Buggy as well as at Central Co-op, Virginia Mason's farmers market - check website for other outlets.
